parameter_templates.name: res
parameter_templates.label: Resolution
parameter_templates.help: Total size of the image, if overscan not set. If not an integer, this sets the Display Window and rounded up to the next pixel for Data Window.

parameter_templates.name: pixelaspectratio
parameter_templates.label: Pixel Aspect Ratio
parameter_templates.help: Width/height of the pixels. Anamorphic is often 2, some old video formats used .9
